<div class=3D"ibis-prose ibis-resource-card__body">
<h1>Online examinations: what to expect</h1>
<p>Candidates can now sit an online training course and gain their qualific=
ation without leaving their home.&nbsp;</p>
<p>To make this possible, we have worked with leading training providers an=
d exam experts to provide a platform that is accessible and easy to use, al=
lowing candidates to focus on passing their exams.</p>
<p>The examinations are taken via APM=E2=80=99s qualification platform, <a =
rel=3D"noopener" href=3D"https://surpass.com/en-gb/test-delivery/" target=
=3D"_blank" title=3D"Surpass">Surpass</a> and the remote invigilation is co=
nducted by <a rel=3D"noopener" href=3D"https://proctorexam.com/test-taker-s=
upport/" target=3D"_blank" title=3D"ProctorExam">ProctorExam</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div data-module=3D"ibis-resource-card" class=3D"ibis-resource-card ">
<div class=3D"ibis-prose ibis-resource-card__body">
<div style=3D"height: 350px; background-color: #d2ddd4; padding: 15px; bord=
er-radius: 5px;">
<div style=3D"height: 110px;">
<h3>Supporting resources</h3>
<ul>
<li><a rel=3D"noopener" href=3D"https://www.apm.org.uk/media/v2vlkgu3/instr=
uctions-for-system-checks-and-setting-up-your-exam.pdf" target=3D"_blank">I=
nstructions: System check and launching exam</a></li>
<li><a rel=3D"noopener" href=3D"https://www.apm.org.uk/media/kgxlni3n/frequ=
ently-asked-questions-remote-invigilated-examinations.pdf" target=3D"_blank=
">Frequently asked questions</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://www.apm.org.uk/about-us/terms-and-conditions/">Exami=
nation Rules and regulations</a></li>
<li><a rel=3D"noopener" href=3D"https://www.apm.org.uk/media/suobcrv3/apm-q=
ualifications-and-standards-candidate-malpractice-policy.pdf" target=3D"_bl=
ank">Candidate Malpractice Policy</a></li>
<li><a rel=3D"noopener" href=3D"https://www.apm.org.uk/media/eaqox4qb/apm-r=
easonable-adjustments-and-access-arrangements-policy.pdf" target=3D"_blank"=
>Reasonable adjustments and access arrangements policy</a></li>
<li><a rel=3D"noopener" href=3D"https://apm.surpass.com/ContentAuthor/testl=
ink/0bd8e29a97c043fd9744741e8c8dbdce" target=3D"_blank" title=3D"PFQ Sample=
 paper">Sample paper: Fundamentals</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"https://apm.surpass.com/ContentAuthor/testlink/588d26a8cae04=
4ba9dbde0822667cd7e">Sample paper: Management (NEW)</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
