<h2 id=3D"rules" style=3D"text-align: center;">How to prepare for an APM on=
line Examination</h2>
<p style=3D"text-align: center;"><div class=3D"fluid-width-video-wrapper" s=
tyle=3D"padding-top: 56.25%;"><iframe src=3D"cid:frame-DA26A19539C130148FD1=
92E950426860@mhtml.blink" frameborder=3D"0" allow=3D"autoplay; fullscreen; =
picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen=3D""></iframe></div></p>
</div>
</div>
<div data-module=3D"ibis-resource-card" class=3D"ibis-resource-card ">
<div class=3D"ibis-prose ibis-resource-card__body">
<h2 id=3D"rules" style=3D"text-align: center;">APM Rules and regulations<br=
><br></h2>
<p style=3D"text-align: center;"><div class=3D"fluid-width-video-wrapper" s=
tyle=3D"padding-top: 56.25%;"><iframe src=3D"cid:frame-D66168A965A57484334D=
F8906D98D073@mhtml.blink" frameborder=3D"0" allow=3D"autoplay; fullscreen; =
picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen=3D""></iframe></div></p>
</div>
