    <div class=3D"it-landing__section" style=3D"background: #e9e9eb" data-t=
heme=3D"">
        <div class=3D"it-landing__row">
<div data-module=3D"ibis-grid" class=3D"ibis-grid it-sigs-and-branches__row=
 iu-padding-top-6 iu-padding-bottom-6" data-size=3D"1/3"><div data-module=
=3D"ibis-resource-card" class=3D"ibis-resource-card " style=3D"grid-column:=
 span 3">
<div class=3D"ibis-prose ibis-resource-card__body">
<h4>Operating System, Browser, Webcam and microphone&nbsp;</h4>
<ul>
<li>Laptop/desktop (please note that you cannot use a tablet or smartphone =
to sit the exam as you need a full operating system).</li>
<li><a rel=3D"noopener noreferrer" href=3D"https://whatsmyos.com/" target=
=3D"_blank" title=3D"Check your operating system">Check your operating syst=
em</a> to ensure you are using Windows 8 (or higher) or MAC OS X and higher=
, ChromeOS and most Linux distributions.&nbsp;</li>
<li>In order to take the examination, you will need to use the latest versi=
on of Google Chrome. Chrome should be <a rel=3D"noopener noreferrer" href=
=3D"https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95417?co=3DGENIE.Platform%3DDe=
sktop&amp;hl=3Den" target=3D"_blank" title=3D"Set your default browser">set=
 up as your default internet browser</a>. <a rel=3D"noopener noreferrer" hr=
ef=3D"https://www.whatsmybrowser.org/" target=3D"_blank" title=3D"Check you=
r browser">Check your browser</a></li>
<li><a rel=3D"noopener noreferrer" href=3D"https://support.google.com/chrom=
e/answer/2693767?co=3DGENIE.Platform%3DDesktop&amp;hl=3Den" target=3D"_blan=
k" title=3D"Ensure microphone and camera allowed in Chrome">Ensure the micr=
ophone and camera are allowed in Chrome</a>. A webcam is required (maximum =
resolution of 1280 x 720), along with a microphone and audio.</li>
<li><a rel=3D"noopener noreferrer" href=3D"https://www.onlinemictest.com/" =
target=3D"_blank" title=3D"Check your microphone">Check your microphone wor=
ks</a>.</li>
<li><a rel=3D"noopener noreferrer" href=3D"https://www.onlinemictest.com/we=
bcam-test/" target=3D"_blank" title=3D"Check your webcam">Check your webcam=
 works</a>.</li>
<li>You must test the same devices that you will be using for the examinati=
on.</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

</div>        </div>
    </div>

    <div class=3D"it-landing__section" style=3D"background: #c7c6cc" data-t=
heme=3D"">
        <div class=3D"it-landing__row">
<div data-module=3D"ibis-grid" class=3D"ibis-grid it-sigs-and-branches__row=
 iu-padding-top-6 iu-padding-bottom-6" data-size=3D"1/3"><div data-module=
=3D"ibis-resource-card" class=3D"ibis-resource-card " style=3D"grid-column:=
 span 3">
<div class=3D"ibis-prose ibis-resource-card__body">
<h4>Smartphone or tablet with camera</h4>
<ul>
<li>Android 8+ and iOS 15.8+ smart devices =E2=80=93 smartphone or tablet =
=E2=80=93 with a camera are supported.</li>
<li>Your smartphone will be used for dual-camera monitoring. This will be a=
ble to show the test taking environment from multiple angles, as well as re=
cording what=E2=80=99s happening on-screen. This offers an enhanced level o=
f security to ensure the integrity of APM examinations.</li>
<li>To enable the dual camera monitoring you will be required to download t=
he ProctorExam app to your mobile phone. The app can be downloaded from the=
 Google Play Store for Android devices and the App Store for iOS (Apple) de=
vices by searching for ProctorExam.&nbsp;<strong>Please do this in advance =
of your exam to ensure that your phone is compatible with the app and that =
you are using the latest version of the app.</strong></li>
<li>If you are using an <strong>iPhone&nbsp;17/17 Pro/Pro Max</strong> plea=
se ensure you phone has been updated to iOS version 26.0.1 to allow you to =
complete the system checks and exam set-up successfully.&nbsp;</li>
<li>When you go to launch your examination, you will be required to scan a =
QR code to enable the dual camera monitoring and to complete the environmen=
t checks.&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

</div>        </div>
    </div>

    <div class=3D"it-landing__section" style=3D"background: #f8f8f8" data-t=
heme=3D"">
        <div class=3D"it-landing__row">
<div data-module=3D"ibis-grid" class=3D"ibis-grid it-sigs-and-branches__row=
 iu-padding-top-6 iu-padding-bottom-6" data-size=3D"1/3"><div data-module=
=3D"ibis-resource-card" class=3D"ibis-resource-card " style=3D"grid-column:=
 span 3">
<div class=3D"ibis-prose ibis-resource-card__body">
<h4>Internet speed</h4>
<ul>
<li>A reliable internet connection is required, as it will be needed for mo=
bile streaming.</li>
<li>We recommend you use an ethernet cable to ensure a more stable connecti=
on or to position yourself as close to the router as possible.</li>
<li>In addition to this switch off/disconnect any other equipment that uses=
 the same network e.g. games consoles, video streaming.</li>
<li><a rel=3D"noopener noreferrer" href=3D"https://www.broadbandspeedchecke=
r.co.uk/" target=3D"_blank" title=3D"Check your internet speed">Check your =
internet speed</a> - we recommend a minimum of 1.5Mbit/s upload, 10Mbit/s d=
ownload, ping under 25 ms.&nbsp;</li>
<li>Tethering to the internet via a mobile phone is not supported.</li>
</ul>
<p style=3D"padding-left: 40px;"><span class=3D"iu-text-size-endnote">Pleas=
e remember that internet and bandwidth speeds can fluctuate.</span></p>
</div>
</div>

</div>        </div>
    </div>

