 span 3">
<div class=3D"ibis-prose ibis-resource-card__body">
<h4>IT Setup</h4>
<ul>
<li>Ensure that you have the latest version of Google Chrome <a rel=3D"noop=
ener noreferrer" href=3D"https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95417?co=
=3DGENIE.Platform%3DDesktop&amp;hl=3Den" target=3D"_blank" title=3D"Set you=
r default browser">set up as your default internet browser</a>.&nbsp;</li>
<li>Setup the ProctorExam <a rel=3D"noopener noreferrer" href=3D"https://ch=
rome.google.com/webstore/detail/proctorexam-screen-sharin/digojkgonhgmnohba=
pdfjllpnmjmdhpg" target=3D"_blank">screen sharing extension</a>. If you are=
 using a Mac please see the instructions on how to <a rel=3D"noopener" href=
=3D"https://www.apm.org.uk/v2/media/eqlbp2s4/update-catalina-for-macos-2.pd=
f" target=3D"_blank">share your screen</a>.</li>
<li>Allow <a rel=3D"noopener" href=3D"https://www.apm.org.uk/media/hikaitzn=
/how-to-enable-pop-ups.pdf" target=3D"_blank">ProctorExam pop-ups</a></li>
<li>Disable software updates (e.g. windows update, software update, etc.). =
Also make sure that you do not have any updates scheduled to occur during y=
our exam.</li>
<li>Due to additional security settings on work laptops/equipment we recomm=
end that you use a personal device.</li>
<li>If you do have to use a work device, check firewalls or security polici=
es with your I.T. Team that might block the exam loading on the day. They m=
ay need to whitelist the following sites:
<ul>
<li><strong>https://surpass.proctorexam.com</strong></li>
<li><strong><a href=3D"https://apm.surpass.com/secureassess/htmldelivery">h=
ttps://apm.surpass.com/secureassess/htmldelivery</a></strong></li>
</ul>
</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Remote examinations can be disrupted by proxy servers, VPN's, network p=
acket inspection/filtering, or strict network security configurations.</li>
<li>APM is not responsible for your IT equipment or internet provision</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

